            <li><strong>Heat Pump:</strong> Higher efficiency, provides both heating and cooling, lower carbon footprint</li>
            <li><strong>Dual Fuel:</strong> Best of both worlds—efficiency plus backup power</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We'll help you evaluate your options based on your home, energy costs, and comfort preferences.</p>

